f=\"/generate\">开始生成</a><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-purple-300 hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/profile\">个人中心</a><a class=\"px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg btn-primary\" href=\"/login\">登录</a></div></div></nav><main class=\"flex-1 pt-16\"><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><section class=\"relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-900/20 via-transparent to-pink-900/20\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-600/20 rounded-full blur-3xl\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-pink-600/20 rounded-full blur-3xl\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full glass-card text-sm text-purple-300 mb-8\"><span class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-pulse\"></span>已支持 Fal.ai 生成</div><h1 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6\"><span class=\"gradient-text\">AI 头像生成</span><br/><span class=\"text-white\">保留你的独特魅力</span></h1><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl text-purple-200/80 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">上传一张照片，即可在 10 秒内生成保留面部相似度的个性化 AI 头像。 15+ 种风格，隐私优先，不存储原图。</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4\"><a class=\"px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold rounded-xl btn-primary\" href=\"/generate\">立即开始生成 →</a><a class=\"px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium rounded-xl glass-card hover:bg-purple-500/10 transition-colors\" href=\"/login\">登录 / 注册</a></div><p class=\"mt-6 text-sm text-purple-300/60\">免费用户每日可生成 3 次 · Pro 用户无限次</p></div></section><section class=\"py-24 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4 gradient-text\">为什么选择 AvatarMe</h2><p class=\"text-purple-200/60 text-center mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">我们专注于质量、隐私和用户体验</p><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-purple-500/5 transition-colors\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🔒</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-white\">隐私优先</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-purple-200/60\">照片仅用于浏览器端特征提取，不上传原图，保护您的隐私。</p></div><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-purple-500/5 transition-colors\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">✨</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-white\">高相似度</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-purple-200/60\">LoRA 微调技术，精确保持面部特征，生成的头像更像您。</p></div><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-purple-500/5 transition-colors\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">🎨</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-white\">多风格</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-purple-200/60\">动漫、游戏、艺术等 15+ 种风格，满足各种场景需求。</p></div><div class=\"glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-purple-500/5 transition-colors\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-4\">⚡</div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-white\">快速生成</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-purple-200/60\">AI 驱动，通常在 10 秒内完成，随时随地生成头像。</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-purple-900/10 to-transparent\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4 gradient-text\">15+ 创意风格</h2><p class=\"text-purple-200/60 text-center mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">从动漫到游戏，从艺术到潮流，找到属于你的风格</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4\"><div class=\"style-card glass-card rounded-xl p-4 text-center cursor-pointer\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-3xl\" style=\"background-color:#f472b620\">🎭</div><p class=\"font-medium text-white text-sm\">日系动漫</p><p class=\"text-xs text-purple-300/60 mt-1\">动漫</p></div><div class=\"style-card glass-card rounded-xl p-4 text-center cursor-pointer\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-3 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-3xl\" style=\"background-color:#06b6d420\">🎭</div><p class=\"font-medium text-white text-sm\">赛博朋克</p><p class=\"text-xs text-purple-300/60 mt-1\">游戏<